snippet.title: Tamil Nadu: Rs 24 crore in Rs 2000 Notes Seized in Vellore

localized.description:
Tamil Nadu: In a raid by Income tax department Rs 24 crore in Rs. 2000 notes seized in Vellore. After demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 this is the biggest raid in which twenty four crores in denomination of Rs 2000 notes.
